A WordPress widget for displaying the most recent twitter status updates for a particular user or users.

At the moment, requires the WordpressZero library to be loaded in your theme: https://github.com/ggilder/wordpress_zero

To-do list:

Sorting & Filtering:
- Sort tweets in multi-user feed
- Filter multi-user results down to the correct number of total tweets

Caching:
- Throttle API requests and use the cache if it's recent

Processing & General:
- Use Twitter API's entities instead of parsing them ourselves (http://dev.twitter.com/pages/tweet_entities)
- Add ability to show each tweet's user


-Gabriel Gilder
